# HomeschoolHQ User Upgrade & Migration Plan
**Customer Journey Through Pricing Tiers**

## Executive Summary

This document defines the upgrade paths, feature unlock sequences, and onboarding flows for users transitioning between HomeschoolHQ pricing tiers. This is the live product customer experience, not a data migration plan.

**Key Principles:**
- Make upgrades feel rewarding, not restrictive
- Show value before asking for payment
- Minimize friction in upgrade flow
- Celebrate tier transitions
- Grandfather early adopters

---

## Upgrade Flow Overview

```
FREE (1 student)
    â†“ [Add 2nd child OR want AI features]
ESSENTIAL ($60/yr)
    â†“ [Need compliance tracking OR work calendar]
PRO ($99/yr)
    â†“ [Want voice logs OR multi-parent access]
PREMIUM ($149/yr)
```

