## Downgrade Scenarios

### User-Initiated Downgrade

**From Pro â†’ Essential:**
```
Downgrade to Essential?

You'll lose access to:
âŒ Compliance dashboard
âŒ Work calendar integration
âŒ AI standard mapping
âŒ Audit reports
âŒ 250GB storage (data over 50GB will be archived)

Your data will be saved for 90 days if you change your mind.

Are you sure?

[Keep Pro] [Downgrade]
```

**From Essential â†’ Free:**
```
Downgrade to Free?

You'll lose access to:
âŒ AI lesson generation
âŒ Curriculum import
âŒ Assessments
âŒ All children except 1
âŒ 50GB storage (data will be archived)

You can still view your data, but editing is limited.

[Keep Essential] [Downgrade]
```

---

### Failed Payment Handling

**Day 1 (Payment Failed):**
- Email: "Payment issue with your subscription"
- Dashboard banner: "Update payment method"
- Grace period: 7 days of continued access

**Day 3:**
- More urgent email
- Modal on login: "Update payment to keep access"

**Day 7 (End of Grace):**
- Features locked
- Email: "Your account has been downgraded to [previous tier]"
- Data preserved for 30 days
- Easy reactivation link

