### Founding Member Pricing (First 100 Users)

**Offer:**
```
Founding Member Special! ğŸ‰

Lock in lifetime pricing:
â€¢ Pro: $79/year (normally $99)
â€¢ Premium: $119/year (normally $149)

Your price NEVER increases as long as you stay subscribed.

[Claim Founding Member Pricing]
```

**Badge:**
- Profile shows "Founding Member â­" badge
- Access to exclusive Slack channel
- Vote on new features

---

### Launch Promotion (First 1,000 Users)

**Offer:**
- 20% off first year
- Price lock guarantee (same as Founding Members)
- "Early Adopter" badge

---

### Referral Program (All Tiers)

**Give $10, Get $10:**
```
Love HomeschoolHQ? Share it!

Give friends $10 off their first year
You get $10 credit per successful referral
Max: $30/year in credits

[Get Your Referral Link]
```

**Implementation:**
- Unique referral URL per user
- Track via URL parameter
- Credits applied to next renewal
- Both parties must be paid subscribers

