### Trial Conversion (Essential Trial)

**Day 1:** "Welcome to your trial"
**Day 3:** "Pro tip: [Feature highlight]"
**Day 7:** "You're halfway through - here's what you've done"
**Day 10:** "4 days left - don't lose your progress"
**Day 13:** "Last chance to keep Essential features"
**Day 14:** Trial expires (final reminder)
**Day 15:** "Your trial ended - we saved your data"

---

### Upgrade Nurture (Free/Essential Users)

**Month 1:** Weekly tips
**Month 2:** Case study (how upgraded user saves time)
**Month 3:** Limited-time offer (20% off upgrade)
**Month 6:** "You've been with us 6 months - here's what you could unlock"

