## Churn Prevention

### At-Risk User Detection

**Signals:**
1. No login for 14 days
2. No lessons created in 30 days
3. Failed payment attempt
4. Clicked "Cancel subscription"

**Action:**
- Email: "We miss you! What can we improve?"
- Offer 1-month free extension
- Survey: "What would make HomeschoolHQ better?"

---

### Win-Back Campaign (Cancelled Users)

**Day 30 After Cancellation:**
- Email: "We saved your data - come back anytime"
- Offer: "50% off for 3 months"

**Day 90:**
- Email: "Final reminder - your data will be deleted in 30 days"
- Last chance offer

**Day 120:**
- Data archived/deleted (with advance notice)

---

