### ESSENTIAL â†’ PRO
- **Target Conversion:** 15% within 90 days
- **Time to Compliance Setup:** <1 hour
- **Calendar Connection Rate:** 60% within 7 days

### PRO â†’ PREMIUM
- **Target Conversion:** 5% within 180 days
- **Voice Log Adoption:** 70% use within 30 days
- **Multi-Parent Invite:** 40% invite co-parent within 60 days

