## Technical Implementation Checklist

### Subscription Management
- [ ] Stripe integration complete
- [ ] Webhook handlers for:
  - [ ] `customer.subscription.created`
  - [ ] `customer.subscription.updated`
  - [ ] `customer.subscription.deleted`
  - [ ] `invoice.payment_failed`
  - [ ] `invoice.payment_succeeded`
- [ ] Prorated upgrades/downgrades
- [ ] Grace period logic (7 days)
- [ ] Data archival automation (30/90 days)

### Feature Gating
- [ ] Middleware checks user tier on every request
- [ ] UI shows locked features with ğŸ”’ icon
- [ ] Click locked feature â†’ upgrade modal
- [ ] Server-side enforcement (no bypassing)

### Trial Management
- [ ] Trial countdown visible in UI
- [ ] Email reminders at 7, 3, 1 days
- [ ] Auto-downgrade on expiration
- [ ] Data preservation logic

### Onboarding Flows
- [ ] Compliance Wizard (Pro tier)
- [ ] Work Calendar OAuth (Pro tier)
- [ ] Feature tour modals (all tiers)
- [ ] Email sequences configured

### Analytics Tracking
- [ ] Track upgrade button clicks
- [ ] Track modal views
- [ ] Track conversion rates
- [ ] Track feature adoption post-upgrade
- [ ] Track churn reasons

